pageContext.claim: “Between Governor @DougDucey of Arizona and Governor @BrianKempGA of Georgia, the Democrat Party could not be happier. They fight harder against us than do the Radical Left Dems. If they were with us, we would have already won both Arizona and Georgia. We received more LEGAL votes by far. All I can do is run, campaign, and be a good (great!) President it is 100% up to the states to manage the election. Republicans will NEVER forget this.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump lost both Georgia and Arizona by narrow margins, but his claims of fraud were never proven in court and the votes were certified.
